The '''1956 [[Syracuse Orange football|Syracuse Orangemen football]] team''' represented [[Syracuse University]] in the 1956 NCAA University Division college football season. The offense scored 230 points, while the defense allowed 11 points. The Orange participated in the Cotton Bowl Classic, which was played on January 1, 1957.
